These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: sailing, lacrosse, cricket, surfing, rugby
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, tiparillo, siglo, blend, pall-mall
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person who's sport is rugby is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Sport      | sailing        | lacrosse | rugby     | cricket   | surfing |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Cigar   | blend  | tiparillo     | oliveros | siglo | pall-mall  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

