.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, lilac, brown, chestnut, coral
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, mouse, rat, dog
 1. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person who likes coral is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the owner of the frog is between the chinese and the fan of techno##2
 6. the owner of the rat is the person who likes lilac##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the indian is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the indian is the person who likes brown##1
12. the owner of the frog is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Color         | chestnut | white | coral    | lilac  | brown    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Pet     | mouse    | frog | dog | rat | guinea-pig |

