.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
The people have 5 different jobs:  architect, manager, pilot, videographer, project-manager
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, lemonade, iced-tea, sprite
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the manager##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
 3. the videographer is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the architect##1
 7. the project-manager is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the pilot is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking fanta is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the project-manager##1
13. the person drinking sprite is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| Job   | pilot      | manager      | videographer       | project-manager       | architect       |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | sprite  | iced-tea    | fanta    | lemonade        |

