There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person who likes grey and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 6. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the colonial house is the person who likes apricot##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes grey is the british##1
11. the townhouse house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
12. the british is on the right of the person who likes red##1
13. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
