.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, roller, scooter, trike, airplane
City: liverpool, nizza, prague, boston, new-york
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, skateboarding, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person traveling to liverpool##2
 5. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Transport   | trike       | airplane       | boat   | scooter      | roller    |
| City       | new-york | boston        | liverpool       | prague       | nizza |
| Job        | writer     | lawyer        | social-worker | dancer        | manager  |
| Sport      | volleyball | skateboarding | climbing      | weightlifting | parkour  |

