 2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the french##1
 5. the palace house is on the right of the cottage house##1
 6. the person drinking water is between the person eating broccoli and the gothic-revival house##2
 7. the craftsman house is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the french##1
10. the victorian house is on the far right##1
11. the person eating onion is between the person eating broccoli and the gothic-revival house##2
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the polish##1
13. the person eating broccoli is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | water      | sprite   | fanta   | soy-milk   |
