 1. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 7. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Birthday       | december        | july   | october  | august   | april |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific       | mystery      | documentary      | epic | fantasy  |

