.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, jet-ski, roller, quad-bike
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, tiparillo, aristoff, old-henry, game
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is between the person watching crime movies and the aristoff-smoker##2
 3. the person driving the roller is the old-henry-smoker##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person driving the roller is between the game-smoker and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the game-smoker##1
10. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Transport      | skateboard      | taxi         | roller      | jet-ski | quad-bike     |
| Cigar           | tiparillo | aristoff | old-henry | game    | siglo  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

