.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
There 5 different types of food: apricot, potato, grapes, lime, avocado
City: edinburgh, hannover, prague, new-york, nizza
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating grapes is between the person driving the airplane and the person eating avocado##2
 8. the person eating potato is between the person eating lime and the person eating apricot##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
10. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Food         | avocado  | grapes | lime   | potato      | apricot |
| City   | edinburgh   | new-york    | hannover | nizza | prague      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish    | cat       | lizard     | mouse      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

