.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, van-climbing, skydiving
5 different games are played: whist, domino, mah-jongg, chess, poker
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, snowmobile, van
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 2. the person playing poker is between the malaysian and the person driving the van##2
 3. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person playing poker is the person driving the bike##1
 5. the person driving the bike is between the thai and the person driving the motorbike##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the person who's hobby is van-climbing is the person driving the car##1
 9. the american is the person driving the car##1
10. the person who's hobby is van-climbing is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person playing domino is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | van-climbing |
| Game   | domino    | poker   | chess | mah-jongg | whist   |
| Transport   | motorbike | bike    | van    | snowmobile       | car         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 